<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; }
        .receipt-card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 500px; }
        .total { font-size: 20px; color: #059669; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Booking Confirmed! 🎉</h2>
<p>Dear <%= customerName %>,</p>
<p>Thank you for your payment. Your stay has been successfully secured.</p>

<div class="receipt-card">
    <h3>Reservation Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> BOOKING- #GPH-000000<%= id %></p>
    <p><strong>Check-in:</strong> <%= checkIn %></p>
    <p><strong>Check-out:</strong> <%= checkOut %></p>
    <p class="total">Total Paid: $<%= totalPrice %></p>
</div>

<p>A formal invoice copy has been saved to your dashboard profile account.</p>
</body>
</html>
